<br>
in general, i'm finding Luclin to be a monk's paradise, at least where solo combat is concerned.  Dawnshroud, for example, is filled with more mushroom creatures who are a suitable, rewarding challenge for a lone monk from 34 to at least 37.  they attack at an amazing range, so there is no need to waste thrown objects or move in too close.  best of all, they grow in groups of three and can be drawn one at a time from the points of their &quot;triad&quot; -- they do not come as a team.  occasionally they'll drop small molds worth 2 - 5 platinum at a very conveniently located merchant camp.  <br>
